    <input name="important" type="text" maxlength="300" placeholder="eg. My god wil not leave me, because i need that faith to keep going." />

    <p>When dealing with my race, I usually...</p>
    <select name="interaction" id="interaction">
        <option value="none" selected>Choose one...</option>
        <option value="nothought">Don't think about it</option>
